    <text type="letter"> 
        <body>
            <pb xml:id="leaf001r" facs="mil.00002.001_large.jpg" type="recto"/>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place">Camden  New Jersey  US America</name>
                    <date when="1888-01-27">Jan: 27 '88<ptr target="mil.00002_n1"/></date>
                </dateline>
            </opener>

            <p>—I have been waiting to get good copies of "Specimen Days" wh' I shall have shortly, &amp; 
                will then immediately send one—I mail "Leaves of Grass" now—the price of the two
                vols. is one pound, wh' I wish you to send me here by p o order (328 Mickle
                Street)—Nothing very new or different—arctic cold here for the last
                fortnight—best regards to you &amp; my Irish friends<ptr target="mil.00002_n2"/>—</p>

            <closer>
                <signed rend="right">Walt Whitman</signed>
            </closer>
            <pb xml:id="leaf001v" facs="mil.00002.002_large.jpg" type="verso"/>
        </body>
